-- West Ham Named First Bidder for London Olympic Stadium
-- B y   D a n i e l l e   R o s s i n g h
-- 2012-12-05T12:48:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-05/west-ham-named-first-bidder-for-london-olympic-stadium.html
West Ham United soccer club was
chosen as the first-ranked bidder to become the new tenant of
the 2012 Olympic Stadium, the London Legacy Development
Corporation said today.  The agency, known as LLDC, oversees the post-Games use of
the London 2012 facilities.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Danielle Rossingh in London at 
 drossingh@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
